new.headline: Partial Recovery of ongoing Service Degradation in West US region

content.excerpt_text: We are currently addressing an issue affecting a portion of the West US datacenter following an unexpected utility power interruption. Backup power systems remain active, and the facility has been fully operational since 12:30 UTC. Both power and physical network connectivity have been restored. Most services in the region are operating normally. Some resources that depend on the previously impacted datacenter may continue to experience degraded availability as storage and compute components...
